1:1: COMMENT NOTE
1:7: STR_LIT "
    斯篇專演「方術」之奧。
    借泰西算學牛頓之法，以漸近求精，
    推求平冪之源（根號二），以驗編譯器「術（函式）」之宣告與施作也。
"
7:1: HERE_ARE i have
7:8: NUMBER_LIT 1
7:10: VAR_TYPE_FUNC func
7:16: NAME_IT name it
7:24: IDENT '牛頓求根法'
7:33: TO_PERFORM_FUNC to perform
7:45: REQUIRE_ARGS requires
7:54: NUMBER_LIT 1
7:56: VAR_TYPE num
7:61: SAID called
7:68: IDENT '試'
7:73: FUNC_BEGIN func begin
8:5: COMMENT NOTE
8:10: STR_LIT " 設甲為初限，啟算之基 "
9:5: HERE_IS_A has a
9:11: VAR_TYPE num
9:15: NUMBER_LIT 1
9:18: NAME_IT name it
9:26: IDENT '甲'
10:5: HERE_IS_A has a
